            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>CDW Corp(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CDW:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CDW\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CDW-US</a>)截至台北時間14日02:52股價上漲6.3美元，報131.83美元，漲幅5.02%，成交量760,955（股），盤中最高價131.83美元、最低價125.25美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.2%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.59%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.83%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+1.05%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>CDW Corp(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CDW:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CDW\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CDW-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+2.89%</li> <li>近 1 月：+10.62%</li> <li>近 3 月：-5.97%</li> <li>近 6 月：-13.45%</li> <li>今年以來：-7.83%</li></ul></section></main>",
